{"tid":1707304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠記者會預告","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:39:57.000Z","uid":81236,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"da6ba0be2c1bb17c10409285f55a921bcdbfbf82","tid":1707304,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"1）警察輪姦 - 唔講<br />\n2）無生命威脅下開槍射人 - 唔講<br />\n3）警察瘋狂駕駛意圖殺人 - 唔講<br />\n4）移動受槍傷人仕身體 - 唔講<br />\n5）721 - 唔講<br />\n6）831 - 唔講<br />\n7）藍絲開的士車人 - 唔講<br />\n8）藍絲多次揸刀斬人 - 唔講<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多 - 統統唔講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到港豬無得返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 大力講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察開槍係示威者迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 大大力講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲被火燒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 大大力講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係咪手足做錯？要割？<br />\n<br />\n唔係！只係手足做得唔夠好，要改善。<br />\n<br />\n唔該你由頭睇到一次唔講既點<br />\n再問下你自己係咪問要唔要割<br />\n<br />\n最後，就算唔講200萬肯遊行民意<br />\n<br />\n單以頭幾點，極權已經再無認受性"},{"pid":"f77781f41e8c8a840d8296322d957594b0af1a08","tid":1707304,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:35:50.000Z","msg":